1. config -> mavenPoject 

2. web.xml
	- springDispatcherServlet 
	- contextConfigLocation 

3. pom.xml (DI 주입) 
	- Spring-webmvc : springMvc 프로젝트를 위해 추가된 dependency
	- Spring-tx : Spring Transaction 사용을 위해 추가된 dependency
	- Spring-orm : JPA를 위해 dependency
	- javax.servlet.jsp.jstl-api : front-end jstl dependency
	- standard : taglib dependency
	- javax.servlet-api : servlet dependency
	- javax.servlet.jsp-api : JSP dependency
	- com.fasterxml.jackson.core : json 변환 dependency
	- mysql
	- junit

4. applicationContext.xml 
	- beans check
	- mvc check
	